## Initialization Sequence

### Complete Initialization Flow

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant Card as CB-LCARS Card
    participant Entry as index.js
    participant CP as ConfigProcessor
    participant PM as PackMerger
    participant Val as ValidationService
    participant MB as ModelBuilder
    participant SM as SystemsManager
    participant TM as ThemeManager
    participant DSM as DataSourceManager
    participant RE as RulesEngine
    participant AR as AdvancedRenderer
    
    Card->>Entry: initMsdPipeline(userConfig, mountEl, hass)
    
    Entry->>CP: processAndValidateConfig(userConfig)
    
    CP->>PM: mergePacks(userConfig)
    PM->>PM: Load builtin packs
    PM->>PM: Load external packs (HTTP)
    PM->>PM: Merge layers with priority
    PM-->>CP: mergedConfig + provenance
    
    CP->>Val: validateMerged(mergedConfig)
    Val->>Val: Schema validation
    Val->>Val: Reference validation
    Val->>Val: Duplicate ID detection
    Val-->>CP: validation issues
    
    CP-->>Entry: { mergedConfig, issues, provenance }
    
    Entry->>MB: buildCardModel(mergedConfig)
    MB->>MB: Resolve anchors
    MB->>MB: Build base model
    MB-->>Entry: cardModel
    
    Entry->>SM: new SystemsManager()
    Entry->>SM: initializeSystems(config, model, mountEl, hass)
    
    SM->>TM: Initialize theme system
    TM->>TM: Load theme tokens
    TM->>TM: Resolve component defaults
    TM-->>SM: Theme ready
    
    SM->>DSM: Initialize data sources
    DSM->>DSM: Subscribe to HA entities
    DSM->>DSM: Preload historical data
    DSM-->>SM: DataSources ready
    
    SM->>RE: Initialize rules engine
    RE->>RE: Parse rule conditions
    RE->>RE: Track dependencies
    RE-->>SM: Rules ready
    
    SM->>AR: Initialize renderer
    AR->>AR: Create SVG container
    AR->>AR: Initialize specialized renderers
    AR-->>SM: Renderer ready
    
    SM-->>Entry: Systems initialized
    
    Entry->>Entry: Create reRender function
    Entry->>Entry: computeResolvedModel()
    Entry->>AR: render(resolvedModel)
    AR-->>Card: Rendered output
    
    Entry->>Entry: Expose window.__msdDebug
    Entry-->>Card: Pipeline ready
```

