## Model Building

### Model Resolution Flow

```mermaid
graph TB
    Base[Base Card Model<br/>From merged config]
    
    subgraph "Resolution Stages"
        Stage1[1. Anchor Resolution<br/>Compute all anchor positions]
        Stage2[2. Theme Application<br/>Apply component defaults]
        Stage3[3. Template Processing<br/>Resolve {datasource} refs]
        Stage4[4. Rules Evaluation<br/>Apply conditional styles]
        Stage5[5. Style Resolution<br/>Merge all style layers]
    end
    
    Final[Resolved Model<br/>Ready for rendering]
    
    Base --> Stage1
    Stage1 --> Stage2
    Stage2 --> Stage3
    Stage3 --> Stage4
    Stage4 --> Stage5
    Stage5 --> Final
    
    TM[ThemeManager] -.provides defaults.-> Stage2
    TP[TemplateProcessor] -.processes templates.-> Stage3
    RE[RulesEngine] -.evaluates rules.-> Stage4
    SRS[StyleResolverService] -.resolves styles.-> Stage5
    
    style Base fill:#f0f0f0,stroke:#666
    style Stage3 fill:#4d94ff,stroke:#0066cc
    style Stage4 fill:#4d94ff,stroke:#0066cc
    style Final fill:#ff9900,stroke:#cc7700,stroke-width:3px
```

### Model Structure

```javascript
// Base Card Model (from config)
{
  id: 'my_msd',
  size: [800, 600],
  theme: 'lcars-classic',
  anchors: { /* anchor definitions */ },
  overlays: [ /* overlay configs */ ],
  rules: [ /* rule definitions */ ],
  routing: { /* routing config */ }
}

// Resolved Model (after all resolution stages)
{
  ...baseModel,
  _resolved: {
    anchors: { /* computed positions */ },
    overlays: [ /* fully resolved overlay configs */ ],
    activeRules: [ /* matched rules */ ],
    themes: { /* active theme tokens */ }
  }
}
```

