## Runtime Updates

### Update Triggers & Flow

```mermaid
graph TB
    subgraph "Update Triggers"
        DS[DataSource Change<br/>HA entity update]
        Rule[Rule Match<br/>Condition becomes true]
        Manual[Manual Update<br/>API call / user action]
        Anim[Animation Complete<br/>Timeline callback]
    end
    
    subgraph "Update Pipeline"
        Check[Check if update needed]
        Resolve[Resolve model]
        Render[Render overlays]
        Notify[Notify listeners]
    end
    
    DS --> Check
    Rule --> Check
    Manual --> Check
    Anim --> Check
    
    Check --> Resolve
    Resolve --> Render
    Render --> Notify
    
    style DS fill:#4d94ff,stroke:#0066cc
    style Rule fill:#4d94ff,stroke:#0066cc
    style Resolve fill:#ff9900,stroke:#cc7700
    style Render fill:#ff9900,stroke:#cc7700
```

### DataSource Update Flow

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant HA as Home Assistant
    participant Entity as Entity Change
    participant DSM as DataSourceManager
    participant DS as DataSource Instance
    participant Buffer as Rolling Buffer
    participant Pipeline as Render Pipeline
    
    HA->>Entity: State change
    Entity->>DSM: stateChanged event
    DSM->>DS: Update datasource
    
    DS->>DS: Get new value
    DS->>Buffer: Add to buffer
    Buffer->>Buffer: Maintain window size
    
    DS->>DS: Apply transformations
    DS->>DS: Calculate aggregations
    DS->>DS: Update computed values
    
    DS->>DSM: Data updated
    DSM->>DSM: Debounce check
    DSM->>Pipeline: Trigger re-render
    
    Pipeline->>Pipeline: Resolve model
    Pipeline->>Pipeline: Render overlays
```

### Rules Engine Update Flow

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant DSM as DataSourceManager
    participant RE as RulesEngine
    participant Rule as Rule Instance
    participant Cond as Condition Evaluator
    participant Pipeline as Render Pipeline
    
    DSM->>RE: Data updated
    
    loop For each rule with dependencies
        RE->>Rule: Check if needs evaluation
        Rule->>Cond: Evaluate conditions
        
        alt All conditions match
            Cond-->>Rule: true
            Rule->>Rule: Mark as matched
        else Some condition fails
            Cond-->>Rule: false
            Rule->>Rule: Mark as not matched
        end
        
        Rule-->>RE: Match status
    end
    
    RE->>RE: Check if matches changed
    
    alt Matches changed
        RE->>Pipeline: Trigger re-render
        Pipeline->>Pipeline: Apply rule styles
    end
```

